text: Gérard Vuilleumier (5 December 1905 - 17 April 1984) was a Swiss ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1928 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1905 births Category:1984 deaths Category:Swiss male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Switzerland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1928 Winter Olympics Category:People from La Chaux-de-Fonds
